      "title": "Police obtain court order against protest planned at Olcott Mawatha",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Police has obtained a court order against a protest demonstration to be staged by a group of Buddhist monks and other religious leaders at Olcott Mawatha today (07).",
        "The court order also prevents them from obstructing or inconveniencing the public, police said."
